CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1778868675
OL,3,CBritish Gas to pay #20m over force-
OL,4,Cfitted prepayment meters scandal
OL,6,FBritish Gas will compensate customers
OL,7,Fwho had a prepayment meter installed
OL,8,Fwithout their permission and issue a
OL,9,F#20 million payout, regulator Ofgem
OL,10,Fhas said.
OL,12,FThe watchdog found that British Gas
OL,13,Ffailed to protect vulnerable customers
OL,14,Fby forcibly fitting the energy meters
OL,15,Finto people's homes before they were
OL,16,Fpaused in 2023.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1778868675
OL,3,CBritish Gas to pay #20m over force-
OL,4,Cfitted prepayment meters scandal
OL,6,FThe energy supplier will compensate
OL,7,Fcustomers who were affected from 2018
OL,8,Fto 2021, in addition to payments
OL,9,Falready made to those affected from
OL,10,F2022 to 2023.
OL,12,FIt will also write off up to #70
OL,13,Fmillion of energy debt for vulnerable
OL,14,Fcustomers as part of the agreement.
OL,16,FThose who are due compensation will be
OL,17,Fcontacted by British Gas and do not
OL,18,Fneed to take action, Ofgem said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1778868675
OL,3,CBritish Gas to pay #20m over force-
OL,4,Cfitted prepayment meters scandal
OL,6,FThe regulator changed the rules on
OL,7,Fprepayment meters in 2023 after the
OL,8,Findustry-wide practice was publicly
OL,9,Fexposed, before launching one of the
OL,10,Fmost complex investigations in its
OL,11,Fhistory.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FThe meters are pay-as-you-go gas and
OL,19,Felectricity systems that can be topped
OL,20,Fup online or with a card at certain
OL,21,Fshops.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1778868675
OL,3,CBritish Gas to pay #20m over force-
OL,4,Cfitted prepayment meters scandal
OL,6,FWhen the money in the meter runs out,
OL,7,Fthe electricity and heating shut off.
OL,9,FThree years ago, it was discovered
OL,10,Fthat, at the peak of the cost-of-
OL,11,Fliving crisis, energy suppliers were
OL,12,Fentering people's homes to forcibly
OL,13,Fswitch them onto prepayment methods.
OL,15,FOfgem then paused the practice, but
OL,16,Flate last year it emerged that
OL,17,Fmagistrates were approving batches of
OL,18,Fwarrants for utility companies to
OL,19,Fbreak into people's homes, including
OL,20,Ffor the fitting of prepayment meters.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1778868675
OL,3,CBritish Gas to pay #20m over force-
OL,4,Cfitted prepayment meters scandal
OL,6,FUnder current rules, suppliers must
OL,7,Fmake at least 10 attempts to contact a
OL,8,Fcustomer and give at least 10 days'
OL,9,Fnotice of a warrant being applied for
OL,10,Fbefore asking a court to approve the
OL,11,Ffitting of a prepayment meter.
OL,13,F"It is clear that British Gas fell
OL,14,Fshort in its treatment of an
OL,15,Funacceptable number of vulnerable
OL,16,Fcustomers who had a prepayment meter
OL,17,Finstalled without consent, and it's
OL,18,Fright that they've taken action to put
OL,19,Fthings right," Ofgem's CEO Tim Jarvis
OL,20,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1778868675
OL,3,CBritish Gas to pay #20m over force-
OL,4,Cfitted prepayment meters scandal
OL,6,F"Because of our actions, customers
OL,7,Fwill receive a substantial package of
OL,8,Fredress, compensation and debt write
OL,9,Foff."
OL,11,FHe added: "The installation of
OL,12,Fprepayment meters under warrant should
OL,13,Fonly be a last resort, with rigorous
OL,14,Fchecks to ensure debt is recovered
OL,15,Flawfully, proportionately and safely."
OL,17,FJarvis told BBC Radio 4's Today
OL,18,Fprogramme he recognised that "clearly"
OL,19,Fthere also needs to be a "way of
OL,20,Frecovering money" from people who do
OL,21,Fnot pay their energy bills.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@EO]sD@KOUwD@fO]|D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1778868675
OL,3,CBritish Gas to pay #20m over force-
OL,4,Cfitted prepayment meters scandal
OL,6,F"We've certainly seen a very big
OL,7,Fincrease in the amount of debt and
OL,8,Farrears in the energy system," he
OL,9,Fsaid, pointing out that "large
OL,10,Fnumbers" of people struggled to pay
OL,11,Ftheir bills amid the energy crisis
OL,12,Fcaused by the war in Ukraine.
OL,14,FChris O'Shea, group chief executive of
OL,15,FBritish Gas owner Centrica, said:
OL,16,F"What happened should never have
OL,17,Fhappened, and I am sorry to the
OL,18,Fprepayment customers who were
OL,19,Faffected. When we get things wrong, we
OL,20,Fmake them right.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1778868675
OL,3,CBritish Gas to pay #20m over force-
OL,4,Cfitted prepayment meters scandal
OL,6,F"When these issues came to light in
OL,7,F2023 ` we apologised, stopped the
OL,8,Factivity immediately and took rapid
OL,9,Faction to improve our processes and
OL,10,Fchange how we engage with customers in
OL,11,Fdebt, particularly those in vulnerable
OL,12,Fsituations.
OL,14,F"Over the last three years, we have
OL,15,Ftreated this matter with the
OL,16,Fseriousness it deserves and have made
OL,17,Fchanges to our practices and put
OL,18,Fsafeguards in place to ensure we
OL,19,Fdeliver the standards our customers
OL,20,Fhave every right to expect."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU|D@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
